<p>This is a quick reference post on updating your local Pi-hole installation, the process can be completed in 3 simple steps:</p>
<h2 id="ssh-into-your-pi">SSH into your Pi</h2>
{% highlight "shell" %}
SSH into your Pi
{% endhighlight %}

<h2 id="check-for-updates">Check for updates</h2>
{% highlight "shell" %}
pihole -v
{% endhighlight %}

<h3 id="run-the-update">Run the update</h3>
{% highlight "shell" %}
pihole -up
{% endhighlight %}

